    "rules1": "Content must be original. Do not steal or reupload others' content.",
    "rules2": "Videos must match the campaign brief you joined.",
    "rules3": "Using bots or cheating methods to boost views is strictly prohibited.",
    "rules4": "Content containing SARA, pornography, or hate speech is strictly prohibited.",
    "rules5": "Any violation will result in account suspension and balance forfeiture."
